com.skratchdot.electribe.model.esx

Interface SongPattern

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SongPatternImpl

    public interface SongPattern
    A representation of the model object 'Song Pattern'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Empty
    • Note Offset
    • Pattern Pointer
    • Position Current

    See Also:
    EsxPackage.getSongPattern()
